mmr_sr <- read_excel("MIMU_BaselineData_AllSectors_Countrywide_18Mar2021_revised.xlsm",
                  sheet = "State_Region",
                  skip = 5) %>% 
  janitor::clean_names() %>% 
  pivot_longer(cols = starts_with("x"), names_to = "year", values_to = "value", values_drop_na = TRUE) %>% 
  mutate(year = str_replace_all(year, "x", ""))
